  "detailed_description": "Help the kitten rescue his friend and other kittens from a spaceship controlled by an evil artificial intelligence.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>80 levels - Play 80 hand-crafted levels filled with deadly traps.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Tight controls - Jump over spikes, climb walls and dash to avoid death with ease, optmized controls for gamepads and keyboards!</li></ul>  <br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Hardcore difficulty - There's no fighting in Kitten Hero, so you'll have to rely on your speed, reflexes to survive!</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Deadly traps - There are a lot types of traps ready to prevent you from saving your friend!</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Cool soundtrack - Your thumbs may hate you, but your ears will love you, lofi 8 bit songs created by Tad!</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Hats - There are 15 different hats for you to collect and custumize your Hero!</li></ul>                                                                         <strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >A high difficulty precision platform game.</h2></strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1813440/extras/4ba0ed001332cbe9bbd3eb014e5eba40.poster.avif?t=1693948744\" width=574 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1813440/extras/4ba0ed001332cbe9bbd3eb014e5eba40.webm?t=1693948744\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1813440/extras/4ba0ed001332cbe9bbd3eb014e5eba40.mp4?t=1693948744\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>                                         <h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Overcome all the challenges created by the A.I. that controls the environment.</strong></h2><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1813440/extras/a7f7087a40b9c19e41615f554546ae6b.poster.avif?t=1693948744\" width=574 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1813440/extras/a7f7087a40b9c19e41615f554546ae6b.webm?t=1693948744\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1813440/extras/a7f7087a40b9c19e41615f554546ae6b.mp4?t=1693948744\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br>                                                                      <h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong> 15 hats to collect and customize your hero</strong></h2><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1813440/extras/ff3d2b7e8308019419c842ee6c515f0f.poster.avif?t=1693948744\" width=574 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1813440/extras/ff3d2b7e8308019419c842ee6c515f0f.webm?t=1693948744\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1813440/extras/ff3d2b7e8308019419c842ee6c515f0f.mp4?t=1693948744\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
